## Styling Rules

### Tailwind Tokens
```
primary     = warm orange/amber (#D4774C approx)
secondary   = accent teal/green
accent      = dark navy (#1A2B4B approx)
warm-50/100/200 = warm beige tones
```

### Typography
- Headings: `font-serif font-bold text-accent`
- Body: `text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-[16px]`
- Labels: `text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold`

### Common Patterns
```tsx
// Section with divider
<section id="section-id" className="mb-12 scroll-mt-20">
  <h2 className="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-accent mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-warm-100">
    Section Title
  </h2>
</section>

// Card
<div className="rounded-xl border border-warm-100 p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary/30 transition-all bg-white">

// CTA Button Primary
<Link href="/tailor-made" className="bg-primary text-white font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90">

// CTA Button Secondary
<Link href="/tours" className="bg-white/15 border border-white/30 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg">
```

